name: DSC 11133
guide:
If alarm raised by single APP, the root cause is someone download rule engine by webconsole:
Server->Connect APP->General Options->RuleEngine->Download Rule.
Other wise, 11156 will be raised at same time, check and fix the invalid rule indicated by 11156

name: DSC 11156
guide: Check the rule indicated by alarm to see if there is consequence defined without filtered by IsExist in condition.
